{"tid":2401053,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"當科學與藝術結合在一起","createTime":"2021-02-09T12:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T04:42:13.000Z","uid":38861,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4576b05ab73cf216db20e5c2cf36d533ffac70b6","tid":2401053,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:07:36.000Z","msg":"我們日常生活所食的大菜糕，裡頭所含有的物質經常性會被用在科學或醫藥用途上。<br />\n<br />\n最常見的例子，就是利用大菜糕所含的Agar加上不同營養及礦物質製成碟狀，用在培植細菌或酵母等用途。<br />\n<br />\n不同品種的細菌或酵母在培養碟上會繁殖成為肉眼可見的圖點，且根據品種的不同將會呈不同的顏色。<br />\n<br />\n以下就是科學家發揮藝術小宇宙的得獎作品：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VfDUAb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfDUAb7.jpg&h=92085341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b50Po5s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb50Po5s.jpg&h=28590653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbomfb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxbomfb7.jpg&h=02c5d989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSGKXqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSGKXqs.jpg&h=cf140218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多作品可參照以下網址：<a href=\"https://asm.org/Events/ASM-Agar-Art-Contest/2020-Winners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasm.org%2FEvents%2FASM-Agar-Art-Contest%2F2020-Winners&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=405cfed0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asm.org/Events/ASM-Agar-Art-Contest/2020-Winners</a>"},{"pid":"215861784b80a5af1f6672eaa2364292b5a37209","tid":2401053,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:08:51.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e222857b4bf2543da170da83be3a65102cf14e","tid":2401053,"uid":135554,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":